cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the SSB absolute frequency to an out-of-range value will cause frequency misalignment and prevent proper SSB transmission and UE synchronization.
du.explanation_zh: 將 SSB 絕對頻率設定為超出範圍的值會導致頻率錯位，並阻止正確的 SSB 傳輸和 UE 同步。
